  <title>Start a new game</title>

  <p>To start a new game:</p>
  <steps>
    <item>
      <p>Press the
      <gui style="button">Play again</gui> button on the right.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>To change the <link xref="board-size">board size</link>, press the
      <gui style="button">Change Difficulty</gui> button on the right.</p>
    </item>
  </steps>

  <note>
  <p>If you are already playing a game and press the <gui style="button">Start
  over</gui> button, <app>Mines</app> will ask if you want
  to <gui>Keep Current Game</gui> or <gui>Start New Game</gui>. If you choose
  the latter, your current game will be lost.</p>
  </note>
